api-1  | Essays
api-1  | What excites you about a career in engineering/technology? Why do you think your abilities and skills are a good fit for
api-1  | Plaksha's B.Tech program?
api-1  | It is my firm belief that the strength of my abilities and skills makes me an ideal candidate for the BTech program at Plaksha University. I am
api-1  | highly self-motivated and hardworking, and possess a strong interest in technology and its applications, which gives me a firm confidence
api-1  | that I would be able to perform well in the fast-paced and challenging setting of Plaksha University. My consistent performance in
api-1  | mathematics and science as evidenced in my grades further cements my capability of succeeding in a technocentric field. For instance, my
api-1  | aggregate performance at high school of 98.6%, inclusive of 99% in Physics, Chemistry and Maths, as well as a perfect 100% performance in
api-1  | Artificial Intelligence, are a testament to my devotion to academics as well as problem solving. These accomplishments are a testament not
api-1  | only to my academic accomplishments but also to my mindset that values seeking new information. Outside of school, I do my best to seek
api-1  | out projects that implement my knowledge and transform it into reality. Projects of this nature correspond to the ideal of Plaksha in terms of
api-1  | being hands-on and innovative in terms of turning ideas into reality. For example, during one of the group-based Smart City projects, we
api-1  | aimed to design one which is fully powered by renewable sources with no use of fossil fuels. This project integrated my interest in
api-1  | engineering with my aim to solve real-world problems in an environmentally friendly way. I also built a personal web page with HTML and
api-1  | CSS, built a text game in Python that demonstrated basic game design, and did data scraping and analysis with Python using Pandas and
api-1  | Matplotlib. The idea of Plaksha’s education being focused on real practical projects is in line with my approach to learning. I will be looking for
api-1  | learning opportunities provided by Plaksha to improve my abilities and make use of my knowledge in the undertakings that will be of great
api-1  | importance. The multidisciplinary and cooperative environment at Plaksha will not only assist me with the improvement of my engineering
api-1  | abilities, but also enable me to search for new ways of solving pressing problems in the world. I also participated in some hackathons and
api-1  | competitions such as Zenith 2022, Codex, and Robotronics 2022 where I also got the chance to advance my teamwork and leadership skills.
api-1  | Also, placing second in the ION 2022 Rising Entrepreneurs contest evidences my ability to remember the significance of working together
api-1  | toward reaching targets in a competitive environment. What I find most appealing in pursuing a career path as an engineer or in the
api-1  | technology field is the prospect of impacting the world utilizing my various capabilities. The opportunities of interacting with different
api-1  | students and professors at Plaksha will definitely Give me the latitude to open my eyes better and to other ideas. Being engaged with such
api-1  | people both in and outside the class will enable me to get a better grasp of education and effective practice to enable me to prepare for the
api-1  | future.
api-1  | Share a time when you contributed to a project or activity that positively affected your school or community. What
api-1  | challenges did you face, and what did you learn about leadership and perseverance?
api-1  | In a recent project names Tenelach organized by DPS School Mathura Road, I led a team of four members to design a smart city powered
api-1  | entirely by clean energy, utilizing solar power, wind energy, geothermal energy, and other sustainable sources to eliminate the use of fossil
api-1  | fuels. Over the course of four weeks, I took responsibility for coordinating the team’s efforts and ensuring the smooth execution of the
api-1  | project.
api-1  | I demonstrated Innovation by leading the team in creating a novel solution for a sustainable smart city that relied entirely on clean energy,
api-1  | showcasing a forward-thinking approach to environmental challenges. When faced with technical difficulties and tight timelines, I remained
api-1  | Resilient, working tirelessly to troubleshoot issues and keeping the team focused on our goal despite setbacks. This helped maintain our
api-1  | momentum and ensured that we could deliver the project successfully.
api-1  | My commitment to Excellence was evident in my dedication to high-quality work. I carefully managed the project’s progress, ensuring every
api-1  | element of the design was meticulously planned and executed, striving for the highest standards in every aspect of the project.
api-1  | I also showed Respect by honoring the contributions of each team member. I fostered a collaborative environment, listening to everyone’s
api-1  | ideas and ensuring that everyone’s voice was heard. This respect extended to the core concept of our project itself, as we aimed to create a
api-1  | model that prioritizes sustainability and environmental respect by eliminating the use of fossil fuels.
api-1  | Finally, I upheld Integrity by being honest and reliable throughout the process. I ensured that communication within the team remained
api-1  | transparent, and I took accountability for my tasks while supporting my teammates in their roles. I remained ethical and committed to our
api-1  | shared goal of creating a clean-energy solution.
